metadata.name: The Ruthless Night Storm
metadata.description:
1 unique single edition NFT 1/1 from collection Eternal Sea.

A mysterious and ruthless force of nature, striking in its beauty.

One of the most mysterious and at the same time commonplace phenomena in nature is the sea storm. Raging waves, furious wind, heavy thunderclouds - all this fascinates and at the same time makes you think. What makes the sea restless? What lurks behind such beautiful and at the same time frightening beauty?

No one knows. And to this day it remains a mystery to all of humankind.

Oil painting into NFT edition

Size: 4382 X 3121 pixels
